    "Details": "<color=#F79B26>The Bellerophon is a failed prototype that was envisioned to complement the Mackie with its higher speed but lacked stability due to its weapon arrangement.</color>\n\nThe BEL-2X attempts to correct the original version by adding endo steel to the chassis along with higher-quality armor and an anti-missile system to keep the 'Mech from becoming too unstable from incoming missile fire. The two Large Lasers are replaced by a pair of Binary Laser Cannons cooled by fifteen double heat sinks. Overall, this improves the Bellerophon's endurance and offensive capabilities, but it does nothing to address its lack of balance.",
